\
The object of this game is survival, pure and simple. As the scorpion, you must do two things well: Find food to bring home, and defend yourself against predators that abound in the maze.\
\
Forage and Fight. Simultaneously, it\'92s even more challenging than it sounds. Because you only have a limited supply of air. \
