Food comes in two forms, Frogs eggs and frogs. \
Eggs naturally come before frogs. If you can locate the eggs and carry them home before they hatch, you will score points very quickly. You will have to be very good, very fast and very lucky to bring home all four eggs, so don\'92t be discouraged when you fail.\
\
But be careful. Because once the eggs hatch into frogs, they become as dangerous as the other predators. \
\
To catch a frog you must first stun him, then Carry him home quickly, because frogs are only stunned briefly. If they wake up, they\'92ll put you to sleep - permanently. \
\
